## 🎨 Customization

### Colors Change Karne ke Liye
`public/css/style.css` file me gradient colors change karein:
```css
background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
```

### Logo Add Karne ke Liye
1. Apna logo `public/assets/logo.png` me dalein
2. `index.html` me add karein:
```html
<img src="assets/logo.png" alt="TRT CHANNEL Logo" class="logo">
```

## 🔒 Security

- YouTube API key Cloudflare Worker me securely store hoti hai
- API key public nahi hoti
- Environment variables ka use hota hai

